data.description: HOME SWEET HOME! This amazing 4 bedroom 2 bath pool home is now available right in the heart of Umatilla! As you are welcomed through the front door you will notice the open floor plan. Large living room, Kitchen with center island and granite countertops plus formal dining are some of the perks to the main living area. Master suite with updated bathroom also features a walk in closet with built-in's. Split bedroom plan with bedrooms #2 and #3. The guest bathroom has a tub/shower combo. The garage was converted to a large 4th bedroom...it also could make a great home office or playroom. Enjoy those hot Florida summer days floating in your pool or you can enjoy watching the kids play in the oversized back yard with play house that conveys. The backyard is fully fence. Enjoy grilling? You will love the covered patio area off of the screen porch that has a built in sink and food prep area. This amazing home will not last long! Call today!
